{
  "text": "Enzymatic activity of purified ACO and ACO/RPE65 proteins were assayed spectrophotometrically by monitoring formation of the all-trans-retinal product at 340 nm using all-trans-b-apo-8 0 -carotenol as the reaction substrate and assay conditions identical to those previously described (Supplementary Material, Fig. S3 ) [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
